summary: An ordinance repealing Ordinance No. 50730, entitled: "An ordinance relating to and providing for the condemnation for street purposes of Lot One (1) Block One (1) in Brygger's Second Home Addition to The City of Ballard, now a portion of the City of Seattle; and providing for the payment thereof", approved the 8th day of April, 1926, and directing the discontinuance of condemnation proceedings heretofore instituted thereunder.
